\c 14
\s Izinto ezithile ezingafanele ukwenziwa emngcwabeni
\p
\v 1 Lingabantwana beN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + Hos. 1.10. Joha. 1.12. Roma 8.16. 9.8,26. Gal. 3.26. 1 Joha. 3.1.\x*. Kaliyikuzisika\x + 1 Kho. 18.28, Jer. 16.6. 41.5. 47.5. 1 Thes. 4.13.\x*, lingenzi impabanga phakathi laphakathi kwamehlo enu ngenxa yabafileyo\x + Levi 19.28.\x*.
\v 2 Ngoba uyisizwe esingcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho; leN\nd kosi\nd* ikukhethile\x + Eks. 19.6.\x* ukuthi ube yisizwe esikhethekileyo kuyo, ngaphezu kwezizwe zonke ezisebusweni bomhlaba\x + 1 Pet. 2.9.\x*.
\s Inyamazana ezihlambulukileyo lezingahlambulukanga
\p
\v 3 Ungadli loba yikuphi okunengekayo\x + Isa. 65.4. Hez. 4.14. Seb. 10.13,14.\x*.
\v 4 Yilezi inyamazana elingazidla: Inkabi, imvu, lembuzi\x + 14.20. Levi 11.2-23.\x*,
\v 5 indluzele\x + 1 Kho. 4.23.\x*, lomziki\x + 1 Kho. 4.23.\x*, lomziki olempondo ezilembaxambaxa\x + 1 Kho. 4.23.\x*, lembuzi yeganga, lomtshwayeli, lenkabi yeganga, legogo\x + Isa. 51.20.\x*,
\v 6 layo yonke inyamazana edabula isondo, edabula okudabukileyo kube zinklagu ezimbili, eyetshisayo phakathi kwezinyamazana; leyo lingayidla.
\v 7 Kodwa lezi kaliyikuzidla kuzo ezetshisayo, lakuzo ezidabula isondo elidabukileyo: Ikamela lomvundla lembila, ngoba ziyetshisa kodwa kazidabulanga isondo; zingcolile kini.
\v 8 Lengulube, ngoba idabula isondo kodwa kayetshisi; ingcolile kini. Lingadli okwenyama yazo, lingathinti izidumbu zazo\x + Levi 11.26.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Lezi lingazidla kuzo zonke ezisemanzini: Zonke ezilempiko lamaxolo lingazidla.
\v 10 Kodwa loba yikuphi okungelampiko lamaxolo lingakudli; kungcolile kini.
\p
\v 11 Zonke inyoni ezihlambulukileyo lingazidla.
\v 12 Kodwa yilezi elingayikudla kuzo: Ukhozi lelinqe lengqungqulu edla inhlanzi,
\v 13 lomzwazwa, lohelwane\x + Levi 11.14.\x*, lelinqe ngohlobo lwalo\x + Isa. 34.15.\x*,
\v 14 lalo lonke iwabayi ngohlobo lwalo,
\v 15 lesikhova, lomandukulo, lenkanku, lokhozi ngohlobo lwalo,
\v 16 isikhova esincinyane, lesikhova esikhulu, lesikhova esimhlophe,
\v 17 lewunkwe, lelinqe elikhulu, letshayamanzi,
\v 18 lengabuzane, lehemu ngohlobo lwalo, lemvenduna, lolulwane.
\v 19 Lazo zonke izibungu ezilempiko zingcolile kini\x + Isa. 34.15.\x*; kazingadliwa\x + Levi 11.21.\x*.
\v 20 Zonke izinyoni ezihlambulukileyo lingazidla.
\p
\v 21 Lingabokudla langcuba; ungayinika owemzini ophakathi kwamasango akho ukuthi ayidle, loba uyithengise kowezizwe\x + Levi 17.15.\x*; ngoba uyisizwe esingcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 14.2.\x*. Ungapheki izinyane lembuzi ngochago lukanina\x + Eks. 23.19.\x*.
\s Umthetho omayelana lokwetshumi
\p
\v 22 Uzanikela ngoqotho okwetshumi kwesithelo sonke senhlanyelo yakho, insimu ekuthelayo iminyaka ngeminyaka\x + 12.6,11,17. Nani 18.21.\x*.
\v 23 Njalo uzakudla phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, endaweni ezayikhetha ukuthi ibeke ibizo layo khona, okwetshumi kwamabele akho, okwewayini lakho elitsha, lokwamafutha akho\x + 14.26. Dute. 12.7,17,18. 12.5.\x*, lamazibulo enkomo zakho lawezimvu zakho, ukuze ufunde ukuyesaba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho insuku zonke\x + 12.6.\x*.
\v 24 Uba-ke indlela inde kakhulu kuwe, uze wehluleke ukukuthwala, ngoba ikhatshana kakhulu lawe indawo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ezayikhetha ukuthi ibeke ibizo layo khona, lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ikubusisile\x + 12.21.\x*,
\v 25 uzakuguqula-ke kube yimali, ubophele imali esandleni sakho, uye endaweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ezayikhetha\x + 2 Kho. 5.23. 12.10.\x*,
\v 26 uthenge ngaleyomali loba kuyini umphefumulo wakho okufisayo, izinkabi loba izimvu loba iwayini loba okunathwayo okulamandla, loba kuyini umphefumulo wakho okufisayo; udle khona phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, uthabe wena lendlu yakho\x + 12.7.\x*.
\v 27 LomLevi ophakathi kwamasango akho, ungamdeli\x + 12.19.\x*, ngoba kalasabelo lelifa kanye lawe\x + 14.29; Nani 18.20.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Ekupheleni kweminyaka emithathu uzakhupha konke okwetshumi kwezithelo zakho ngalowomnyaka, ukugcine phakathi kwamasango akho\x + 26.12. Amos 4.4.\x*.
\v 29 LomLevi\x + 26.12. Amos 4.4.\x*, lokhu engelasabelo lelifa kanye lawe\x + 14.29. Nani 18.20.\x*, lowemzini, lentandane, lomfelokazi, abaphakathi kwamasango akho, bazakuza, badle, basuthe, ukuze iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ikubusise emsebenzini wonke wesandla sakho owenzayo\x + 15.10. 24.19. Hlab. 41.1. Zaga 14.21. 19.17. 22.9. Mal. 3.10.\x*.